\lvert f(\lambda)\rvert = \left\lvert \sum_{k=-m}^m t_k e^{ik\lambda} \right\rvert \leqslant \sum_{k=-m}^m \lvert t_k\rvert\cdot \left\lvert e^{ik\lambda}\right\rvert = \sum_{k=-m}^m \lvert t_k\rvert.
